data.description: Searching for your dream home, look no further! This immaculate end-unit townhome offers an open concept design creating a spacious and cozy atmosphere in a prime location. This beautiful 3-level home features 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths of incredible space and a ton of storage. The terrace level, which is located off the 2-car garage, can be utilized as an extra-large bedroom or an extra space for entertaining/recreation room, and features a full ensuite bathroom, walk-in closet, fireplace, and a rear private entrance leading out to the covered patio and backyard. The main floor offers a spacious open floor plan starting with a large great room that opens into a formal dining space and kitchen, between which is a beautiful double-sided fireplace. The kitchen features stainless steel GE appliances, built-in microwave, convection oven, granite countertops, hooded gas range, and a center island with breakfast bar. Off the kitchen is an informal dining area, powder room, and access to the large, covered deck that is perfect for entertaining year-round and features a wooded view with plenty of privacy. The deck offers the perfect space for rest and relaxation. The main floor features impeccable hard wood floors, and other elegant details including wainscoting, built-in shelving, and custom trim. On the third floor the 3 remaining bedrooms can be found including the owner's suite, along with the laundry room, and another full bathroom. The oversized owner's suite features trayed ceilings and an ensuite bathroom with double vanities, large tub with custom leaded glass window, frameless shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. With tons of windows throughout the home, the space feels light and has a welcoming ambiance perfect to call home. The Woodlands Preserve is a friendly gated community featuring a swimming pool, gazebo, and club house. This townhome is in the absolute perfect location, with a short walk directly across the street to Avalon, which can be accessed by a gate in the subdivision! In addition, the neighborhood is located within minutes of downtown Alpharetta, incredible restaurants, shopping, entertainment, parks, Alpha Loop, easy access to Georgia 400, and so much more!
